Dependencies
------------

- libcurl (w/ SSL support)

Compile
-------

# ./waf configure
# ./waf
# sudo ./waf install

Usage
-----

cprowl : prowl client
  usage:
    cprowl [-a apikey] [-n appname] [-e event] [-d description] [-p priority]

    apikey:
      prowl api key

    appname:
      string : application name (default: "cprowl")

    event:
      string : event name (default: "event")

    description:
      string : description (default: "")

    priority:
      -2 : very low
      -1 : moderate
       0 : normal (default)
       1 : high
       2 : emergency
